  "title": "Order Processing Executive - WCAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Managed the end-to-end order-to-delivery process, including purchase order handling and shipment coordination.</li>\n  <li>Oversaw customer accounts, tracked shipments and revenue, and reviewed raw material needs and customer forecasts.</li>\n  <li>Acted as the primary liaison for customers, coordinating with internal teams to meet service and delivery expectations.</li>\n  <li>Handled customer inquiries and resolved order fulfillment issues promptly and professionally.</li>\n  <li>Collaborated with cross-functional teams to improve production planning and streamline logistics workflows.</li>\n  <li>Planned and monitored demand and supply to ensure accurate forecasting and balanced inventory.</li>\n  <li>Analyzed supply and demand trends to anticipate needs and proactively address potential challenges.</li>\n  <li>Supported the implementation of new processes and continuous improvements to enhance operational efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Maintained product configurations and Bills of Materials (BOMs) within the fulfillment system.</li>\n  <li>Prepared and analyzed reports to support business planning and departmental decision-making.</li>\n  <li>Ensured accurate data management and reporting for process optimization.</li>\n  <li>Carried out additional responsibilities and tasks as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Nyon Hock Sen (Aden)</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124070</p>",
